name: Private Art Lessons with Lauren!
description:
Private art lessons allow the student highly personalized instruction on the topic of your choice. This is perfect for a K-12 or college student who might need extra help to get through classes or the continuing education student who is ready for the next step in their art career. If you've never taken an art class, a private lesson is a great way to get a thorough introduction to the subject matter. Private lessons make a great gift for the artist in your family. 

Currently I teach lessons are available in drawing, ceramics, and the Adobe Creative Suite. Lessons in ceramics and drawing include all materials. Lessons in Adobe Creative Suite require a computer and access to the software. 

Ceramics lessons are taught in my studio in Lakewood, Ohio. Drawing and Adobe Creative Suite can be taught at my studio or your home.

name: Group Art Lessons with Lauren!
description:
Small group art lessons allow for highly personalized instruction within a group atmosphere on the art topic of your choice. This is perfect for a group of home schooled, K-12 or college students who might need extra help to get through classes or a small group of continuing education students who are ready for the next step in their art career but want to continue learning in a group dynamic. A group lesson is not just for students! Group lessons are a great family, friend, or corporate activity. Are you looking for an exciting way to engage your office in team building activities? Sign them up for a group lesson in ceramics. Group lessons make a great gift for the artists in your family-treat your kids or parents to a small group art lesson for the holidays! 

My class sizes are no bigger than four people so that I can give proper demonstrations and focus on each student. If your family is larger than four or you are interested in a corporate event, birthday party, etc., please contact me for specific pricing.

Currently I teach lessons are available in drawing, ceramics, and the Adobe Creative Suite. Lessons in ceramics and drawing include all materials. Lessons in Adobe Creative Suite require a computer and access to the software. 

Ceramics lessons are taught in my studio in Lakewood, Ohio. Drawing and Adobe Creative Suite can be taught at my studio or your home.
